column8: Partly cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of light showers during the morning and afternoon. Light winds becoming south to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h in the middle of the day then becoming light in the evening.
Partly cloudy. The chance of fog in the early morning. Light winds becoming southeast to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h in the early afternoon then becoming light in the evening.
Areas of morning fog. Mostly cloudy day. Slight (20%) chance of a shower in the northwest suburbs. Light winds becoming southerly 15 to 25 km/h during the day then becoming light during the evening.
Patchy morning fog in the southeast suburbs. Partly cloudy day. Slight (20%) chance of a shower. Winds south to southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h.
Humid. Cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers. Winds southeast to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h tending east to southeasterly during the morning.
Cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers. Winds southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h turning southerly 25 to 40 km/h during the morning.
Cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. Winds southerly 20 to 30 km/h turning southeasterly 25 to 40 km/h during the morning.
